---
title: Portobello Mushroom Fajita Mushroom Fajita with Beans and Salsa
description: When you’re looking for a meaty taste, but don’t fancy the meat, Portobello mushrooms are the way to go. Their flavour is rich and earthy, and they’re the perfect match for stronger flavours, making them great with the kick of Mexican spice in this recipe!
